text:
Great job!
You really improved in the second half!

The photographer praised
your expressions, Mano.

...Thank you.
It's thanks to you, Producer-san.

Haha, did the strategy of imagining the
other person as a bird work out?

Y-Yes,
that might have helped... Also...

I was really happy that you encouraged
me and thought about me, Producer.

Haha... Well, yeah,
if I could be of any help to you, Mano, then I'm happy too.

Yes... From now on, whenever I feel nervous,
I'll remember this strategy...
